metadata.name: Fractal-gasm
metadata.description:
Fractal-gasm by Nuwan Shilpa Hennayake

Absorbed in mindless contemplations of infinity and complex patterns of self-similarity! 
(Sometimes I think) 
All we all just driven by recursivity, oscillating in between familiar realities?
(Sometimes I ponder) 
In the presence of the Mysterium Tremendum, wondering if it's nothing but a fractal-gasm!

2160 x 2160 | 24 fps | 11 second | .mp4
